headline: Is Grainger (GWW) Pricing Leave Room After 5-Year 184% Share Price Gain
summary: If you are wondering whether W.W. Grainger at around US$1,033 per share is priced for perfection or offering any value, this article walks through what the current market price might be implying. The stock has returned 2.4% over the last week and 7.8% over the last month, while the year to date return is 2.9% and the 1 year return shows a 2.5% decline, set against a very large 5 year gain of 184.8%. Recent attention on W.W. Grainger has centred on its role as a large industrial distributor...
